02:36.120 --> 02:38.873
Careful, you almost hit that anthill.

02:38.920 --> 02:43.152
And even these tiny creatures
are very important to our ecosystem.

02:44.200 --> 02:48.273
Pick your poison, Truscott.
You're getting a buzz cut either way.

02:49.080 --> 02:50.433
l pick

02:51.760 --> 02:52.795
